<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> pūviṉ kiḻatti mevi viṟṟiruppa metiṉimātu nitiyiṟpuṇara vayappormaṭantai
<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yappuyattiruppa mākkalai maṭantai vākkiṉil viḷaṅkat ticaiyirunāṉku micai
<lb n="3"/>nila veṟippa Aṟaneṟi vaḷara maṉuneṟi tikaḻa Aṟaneṟiccamaiyaṅka ḷāṟun taḻaippa kāṉave
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṅkaiyai villuṭaṉ turantu miṉaṅ kaṉakācaṉattu viṟṟiruppa veṇkiri cūḻnta veḻ kaṭale<note n="58-1">Stops here.</note> 
</p>

